description: Ework Group AB engages in the provision of consultancy services within information technology, telecommunications, technology, and business development sectors. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 276 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2008-05-22. Its services are provided to four business areas: information technology (IT), telecommunication, technology and business development. The firm matches consultants to assignments by offering an access to a consultant network. The company offers three types of collaboration: Consultant brokerage, Consolidated consultant delivery and Outsourced consultant delivery. In addition, It provides systems, administration and management support related to the assignment. The firm collaborates with Sony Mobile Communications, Nasdaq OMX, TetraPak and Tieto. The company operates in Sweden, Finland, Denmark and Norway, through its three wholly owned subsidiaries: eWork Nordic OY, eWork Danmark ApS and eWork Norge AS.
